**Candidates Storage:**
- Currently in-memory array (12 mock candidates)
- Mock data includes realistic profiles with videos from pexels.com
- No Prisma integration yet

**Upload Handler:**
- Filesystem-based, local `./uploads/` directory
- Timestamp + UUID naming scheme
- Content-Type detection for 12 file types (pdf, images, video, docs)
- No size limits or validation

**Entry Point (index.ts):**
```typescript
import "dotenv/config";
import { serve } from "@hono/node-server";
import { app } from "./app.js";

const port = Number(process.env.PORT) || 3001;

serve({ fetch: app.fetch, port }, (info) => {
  console.log(`API server running on http://localhost:${info.port}`);
});
```

Uses `@hono/node-server` (Hono's native Node.js adapter)

